VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (?:Start-Process|&\s+cmd(?:\.exe)?|Invoke-Command)\s+[^`\n]*\$(?:args|input|params|\w+URL|\w+Path|\w+Cmd)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:EscapeShellArgument|Sanitize|\[ValidatePattern\]
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects process invocation with variable arguments that may contain unsanitized input.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Start-Process or cmd.exe with Variable Arguments.
